--- !u!114 &11400000
MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInstance: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 4298c1582b1a1b6428acd6f21334c2fe, type: 3}
  m_Name: VillageChief_DialogueData
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::DialogueData
  nameText1:
    nameVI: "Gi\xE0 l\xE0ng"
    nameEN: Village Chief
  nameText2:
    nameVI: Fu
    nameEN: Fu
  dialogueLines:
  - image: {fileID: 6267887428032955541, guid: e29a4cb30ed02504ca81afbc3db9a8a2, type: 3}
    IsChar1: 1
    textVI: "C\xE1i th\u1EB1ng tr\u1EDDi \u0111\xE1nh! Tao t\u01B0\u1EDFng m\xE0y
      ch\u1EBFt r\u1EE5c \u1EDF x\xF3 x\u1EC9nh n\xE0o r\u1ED3i ch\u1EE9? Sao kh\xF4ng
      bi\u1EBFn khu\u1EA5t m\u1EAFt kh\u1ECFi c\xE1i l\xE0ng n\xE0y lu\xF4n \u0111i
      cho r\u1EA3nh n\u1EE3?"
    textEN: "You damn brat! I thought you\u2019d kicked the bucket in some ditch
      by now. Why don't you just disappear from this village for good?"
    autoSkip: 0
  - image: {fileID: 5921392838902934559, guid: 57d488ea8999ace48ba1a026ea0c1892, type: 3}
    IsChar1: 0
    textVI: ...
    textEN: ...
    autoSkip: 0
  - image: {fileID: 6267887428032955541, guid: e29a4cb30ed02504ca81afbc3db9a8a2, type: 3}
    IsChar1: 1
    textVI: "Cha m\u1EB9 m\xE0y \u0111\xFAng l\xE0 m\u1EAFt m\xF9 m\u1EDBi nh\u1EADn
      nu\xF4i c\xE1i th\u1EE9 nh\u01B0 m\xE0y. Sao c\xE1i ng\u1ECDn l\u1EEDa h\xF4m
      qua kh\xF4ng thi\xEAu ch\u1EBFt qu\xE1ch hai ng\u01B0\u1EDDi h\u1ECD \u0111i
      cho r\u1ED3i, \u0111\u1EE1 ph\u1EA3i kh\u1ED5 v\xEC m\xE0y!"
    textEN: "I\u2019ll never understand what your parents were thinking when they
      took you in. Why didn\u2019t that fire just take them both out and spare them
      the trouble of you?"
    autoSkip: 0
  - image: {fileID: 5921392838902934559, guid: 57d488ea8999ace48ba1a026ea0c1892, type: 3}
    IsChar1: 1
    textVI: ...
    textEN: ...
    autoSkip: 0
  - image: {fileID: 6267887428032955541, guid: e29a4cb30ed02504ca81afbc3db9a8a2, type: 3}
    IsChar1: 1
    textVI: "V\u1EC1 r\u1ED3i th\xEC li\u1EC7u m\xE0 y\xEAn ph\u1EADn, \u0111\u1EEBng
      c\xF3 g\xE2y th\xEAm phi\u1EC1n ph\u1EE9c. Nh\xE0 tao ph\xEDa sau kia v\u1EABn
      c\xF2n \xEDt \u0111\u1ED3 kh\xF4 d\u1EF1 tr\u1EEF, c\u1EA5m m\xE0y b\xE9n m\u1EA3ng
      t\u1EDBi \u0111\xF3 m\xE0 \u0103n tr\u1ED9m nghe ch\u01B0a!"
    textEN: "Now that you're back, stay out of trouble. I've got some food supplies
      stashed at my house\u2014don\u2019t you dare think about 'stealing' any!"
    autoSkip: 0
  - image: {fileID: 5921392838902934559, guid: 57d488ea8999ace48ba1a026ea0c1892, type: 3}
    IsChar1: 0
    textVI: "Con bi\u1EBFt r\u1ED3i. Con c\u1EA3m \u01A1n tr\u01B0\u1EDFng l\xE0ng."
    textEN: 
    autoSkip: 0
  - image: {fileID: 6267887428032955541, guid: e29a4cb30ed02504ca81afbc3db9a8a2, type: 3}
    IsChar1: 1
    textVI: "Ai th\xE8m c\xE1i \u01A1n c\u1EE7a m\xE0y! C\xE1i t\xEAn kh\u1ED1n \u0111\xE3
      t\xE0n ph\xE1 l\xE0ng m\xECnh \u0111ang \u1EDF ph\xEDa \u0110\xF4ng \u0111\u1EA5y.
      Sao m\xE0y kh\xF4ng ch\u1EA1y \u0111\u1EA1i t\u1EDBi \u0111\xF3 r\u1ED3i ch\u1EBFt
      lu\xF4n \u0111i cho khu\u1EA5t m\u1EAFt tao?"
    textEN: "Hmph! Who needs your thanks? The bastard who laid waste to this village
      is off to the East. Why don\u2019t you just run over there and get yourself
      killed already?"
    autoSkip: 0
  - image: {fileID: 5921392838902934559, guid: 57d488ea8999ace48ba1a026ea0c1892, type: 3}
    IsChar1: 0
    textVI: "Con c\u1EA3m \u01A1n \xF4ng. Con v\u1EC1 b\xE1o tin cho cha m\u1EB9
      xong... s\u1EBD \u0111i ngay."
    textEN: "Thank you, Chief. I\u2019ll go check on my parents, then I\u2019ll be
      on my way"
    autoSkip: 0
  - image: {fileID: 6267887428032955541, guid: e29a4cb30ed02504ca81afbc3db9a8a2, type: 3}
    IsChar1: 1
    textVI: "C\xE1i g\xEC? M\xE0y \u0111\u1ECBnh \u0111i th\u1EADt \xE0? M\xE0y m\xE0
      \u0111i th\xEC c\xE1i \u0111\u1ED1ng \u0111\u1ED5 n\xE1t n\xE0y ai x\xE2y l\u1EA1i
      cho tao? \u1EDE l\u1EA1i ngay!"
    textEN: "Hey! You\u2019re actually leaving? If you go, who\u2019s going to rebuild
      this mess? Stay right where you are!"
    autoSkip: 0
  - image: {fileID: 5921392838902934559, guid: 57d488ea8999ace48ba1a026ea0c1892, type: 3}
    IsChar1: 0
    textVI: ...
    textEN: ...
    autoSkip: 0
  - image: {fileID: 6267887428032955541, guid: e29a4cb30ed02504ca81afbc3db9a8a2, type: 3}
    IsChar1: 1
    textVI: "H\u1EEB! M\xE0y mu\u1ED1n l\xE0m g\xEC th\xEC l\xE0m, l\xE3o gi\xE0
      n\xE0y kh\xF4ng th\xE8m c\u1EA3n n\u1EEFa. C\xE1i l\xE0ng n\xE0y tao lo ch\u01B0a
      xong, gi\u1EDD l\u1EA1i c\xF2n ph\u1EA3i t\u1ED1n c\u01A1m nu\xF4i cha m\u1EB9
      m\xE0y n\u1EEFa... \u0110\xFAng l\xE0 n\u1EE3 \u0111\u1EDDi!"
    textEN: "Hmph. Do whatever you want, I\u2019m done stopping you. I\u2019ve got
      enough on my plate with this village, and now I\u2019ve gotta waste more food
      on your parents... What a pain."
    autoSkip: 0
  endDialogue: 
  autoProgressDelay: 1.5
  typingSpeed: 0.05
  voiceSound: {fileID: 0}
  voicePitch: 1
